      <pubtit>Leveraging LSTM models for overlap detection in multi-party meetings</pubtit>
      <p><img src="http://localhost:4000/images/pubpic/STS_news.png" class="img-responsive" width="33%" style="float: left" /></p>
      <p>We succeeded in measuring the superfluid density with atomic resolution on an unconventional superconductor! In contrast to expectations for conventional superconductors, we find that the superfluid densisty is strongly inhomogeneous in FeTe0.55Se0.45.</p>
      <p><em>Neeraj Sajjan, Shobhana Ganesh, Neeraj Sharma, Sriram Ganapathy, Neville Ryant</em></p>
      <p><strong><a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8462548">Nature 571, 541 (2019)</a></strong></p>
